com.intel.fightclub.dialog.state

Class CUIListenerWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.state.CUIListenerWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CUIListener

    @ThreadSafe
public final class CUIListenerWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements CUIListener
    Wraps a CUIListener implementation so that it runs on the thread that created an instance of this class.

      • onRegistered

        public void onRegistered(@NonNull
                         CUIState state)
        Description copied from interface: CUIListener

        This is called when a CUIListener instance is registered with the DialogManager. This provides a CUIState object which contains information about the current state of the CUI.

        This is guaranteed to be called before any other callback.

        Specified by:
        onRegistered in interface CUIListener
        Parameters:
        state - The current state of the CUI.
